<h2>What a Good Business Website Includes</h2>

<p>At minimum, your website should have:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Clear description of your services or products</strong></li>
  <li><strong>Contact information</strong> - phone, WhatsApp, email, location</li>
  <li><strong>Mobile-friendly design</strong> - over 80% of Nigerian web traffic is mobile</li>
  <li><strong>Fast loading speed</strong> - if it takes more than 3 seconds, visitors leave</li>
  <li><strong>SSL certificate</strong> - the padlock icon that shows your site is secure</li>
  <li><strong>Privacy policy</strong> - required by the NDPA</li>
  <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> - so you know who visits and where they come from</li>
</ul>

